OL,3,C'Get on' with fixing the 'broken
OL,4,Croads', Keir Starmer tells councils
OL,6,FSir Keir Starmer has urged councils to
OL,7,F"get on with the job" of fixing
OL,8,Fpothole-plagued roads, which he warned
OL,9,F"can risk lives and cost families
OL,10,Fhundreds if not thousands of pounds on
OL,11,Frepairs".
OL,13,FThe prime minister made the comments
OL,14,Fas the Department for Transport (DfT)
OL,15,Fannounced how much each local
OL,16,Fauthority in England will receive to
OL,17,Fmaintain roads in the next financial
OL,18,Fyear.
