OL,6,FThe Treasury announced in the Budget
OL,7,Fin October that total local road
OL,8,Fmaintenance funding in 2025/26 will be
OL,9,Fnearly #1.6 billion, representing a
OL,10,F#500 million uplift compared with the
OL,11,Fprevious 12 months.
OL,13,FThe funding allocations include:
OL,15,FThe increase is estimated to be enough
OL,16,Fto fix around seven million potholes.
