OL,3,C'Get on' with fixing the 'broken
OL,4,Croads', Keir Starmer tells councils
OL,6,FStarmer said: "Broken roads can risk
OL,7,Flives and cost families hundreds if
OL,8,Fnot thousands of pounds on repairs.
OL,9,FThat's a cost that can easily be
OL,10,Favoided by investing properly in our
OL,11,Froads.
OL,13,F"Through our Plan for Change we're
OL,14,Fdetermined to put more money back into
OL,15,Fthe pockets of hardworking people and
OL,16,Fimprove living standards.
