OL,3,C'Get on' with fixing the 'broken
OL,4,Croads', Keir Starmer tells councils
OL,6,F"That's why we're giving councils
OL,7,Ffunding to repair our roads and get
OL,8,FBritain moving again ` with a clear
OL,9,Fexpectation that they get on with the
OL,10,Fjob."
OL,12,FThe cost of bringing pothole-plagued
OL,13,Flocal roads in England and Wales up to
OL,14,Fscratch has been estimated at #16.3
OL,15,Fbillion.
OL,17,FRAC figures show drivers encounter an
OL,18,Faverage of six potholes per mile on
OL,19,Froads in England and Wales and the
OL,20,Fcost per incident of pothole damage to
OL,21,Fvehicles is around #500.
