OL,3,C'Get on' with fixing the 'broken
OL,4,Croads', Keir Starmer tells councils
OL,6,FHe said: "With most journeys starting
OL,7,Fand ending on local roads, it is vital
OL,8,Fto restore the structural integrity of
OL,9,Fthe streets we live on.
OL,11,F"We urge councils to focus on
OL,12,Fpermanent and innovative repairs
OL,13,Frather than adopting a 'patch and run'
OL,14,Fapproach."
OL,16,FThe Local Government Association,
OL,17,Fwhich represents councils, was
OL,18,Fapproached for a comment.
